Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之骰一經擲出　就已無法停止轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:50.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅之風揚　我只欲逆風直上
