Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利的死訊很快傳到了天城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據哲力胥艦隊來報 方修利確已死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將遵從殿下的命令 即日返航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉告哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行不辱使命 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥 你違背了對媽媽的誓言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時 當時你說得那麼好聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是孩兒無能 沒能生擒那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但母親大人 請您務必保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我怎麼能冷靜得下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 屍體 屍體總有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手把他碎屍萬段 替亞瑟斯報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很遺憾 屍體過後才能送來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上掉頭回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你空手回來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是藩王殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個孩子 你這個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個不孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1328,850)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}艾斯塔爾的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗大人 據說方修利去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個戰術家會這樣輕易死去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 您是說他還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想必正藏身於艾斯塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待時機逃往其它行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蘭西亞 來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來法爾過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於能獨當一面了 可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想快點回信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒什麼好話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 要去工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然不知能不能作為信中話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有段時間會沒法見公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒有考慮方修利還活著的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去負責遺體交接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一方修利還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把他抓回來領功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於此事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗閣下主動請求負責交接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下已經批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他搶先了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 渚士朗卿的原副官正在盧塔西禁閉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他身邊不太平？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在先前的叛亂未遂事件中有人受到牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說正怨恨著身為艾斯特拉德侯公子的法爾密子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿來做文章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一處就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在官邸的警備配置上暗中開一個缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解渚士朗卿的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到原副官的死訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能會辭掉此次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星艾斯塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星エスタール
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔爾政府完全封鎖了整個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一隻老鼠都逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓他們誇下海口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把提督的遺體交給泰坦尼亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而關鍵的遺體不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被我活著逃出了這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球可真是萬事休矣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想聽到什麼「大概能」之類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真能逃出去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早預料到了這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒早晚會放鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 反正我們有得是儲備糧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的巧克力可能會剩下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直覺罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺機會可能很快就會來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}法爾密子爵府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー子爵邸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會被伊德里斯卿的部下保護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生活也很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主也很擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起公主 她已經在信上寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說會沒法見到渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也想通知你一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 我也想同往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 還請多多當心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 法爾密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿只受了點擦傷 逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手下當場逮捕了不逞之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方無疑是叛亂份子的殘黨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情正在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在您的管轄之下居然會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是警衛人手不足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了 我方的警備是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會加強戒備…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向藩王殿下提議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此次事件為戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭取解除法爾密卿的緊閉處分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請派他作為和艾斯塔爾的交涉輔佐同往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且在適當的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照伊德里斯卿先前的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派他前往周邊星域赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是比禁閉更重的發配邊疆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣既能保證他的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不會給伊德里斯卿添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這確實是我提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但渚士朗卿是不信任我的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若殿下不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就交給你處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 同意渚士朗卿的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的計劃居然全盤落空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於渚士朗卿從中斡旋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密再次回到了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副官大人 別來無恙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說客套話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事結果加重了你受的處分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我擅自主張 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有所覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起身上開個洞 這算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿之所以要去艾斯塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只需確認遺體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿和法爾都走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 還請暫且忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位很快都會回天城的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直陪著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蘭西亞 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}埃爾伯特·卡納庫大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルベルト・カナック大統領
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 泰坦尼亞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 這麼快就等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是情報洩漏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有相關跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但下官擔心對方艦隊會發現我方的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是著名的智將渚士朗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被他抓住馬腳就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問如何處置？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬上解除艦隊對星球的封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣一來 萬一被方修利逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續封鎖宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有船從其它地方逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是方修利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然不知道他本人是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 下官馬上去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備一口棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況有變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼新動向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的艦隊馬上會來取提督的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔爾政府急忙解除了封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是誰來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是四公爵中最有心計的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督和他誰更有心計
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我的研究題目之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心計嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很討厭這個對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟機不可失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡力而為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能順利交接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據對方的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計會有一番辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿做得也真過火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來會拖入持久戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿就按計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾斯塔爾大總統官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エスタール大統領官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡納庫大總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在下來得突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您還是抽空接見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩渚士朗卿親自前來 不勝光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也看到那副慘狀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在貴方謝罪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上我國的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會和泰坦尼亞握手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解貴國的主張了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在交涉之前能先確認遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 關於移送天城一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您不要誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前確實談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但哲力胥卿後來攻擊我國 揚長而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若貴國不對侵略我國主權進行道歉和賠償…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不移交遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我並不是為謝罪而來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就沒必要談了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是全無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揣測交涉對象的氣量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這點來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延時間才是閣下的本意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴國的宇宙港為什麼封鎖著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利一派還有殘黨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要瞞著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有義務告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要動用軍隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿 請快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說艾斯塔爾軍發現了方修利的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜祭出空城計爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於您的信念 在下拜服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的蒼蠅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抓住方修利…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真是永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗正在艾斯塔爾交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方群龍無首 總會有辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和傳言中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦散開 封鎖目標的退路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮第二次齊射 瞄準完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威懾攻擊 不要命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓對方停船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔爾艦隊從前方快速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前門拒虎 後門進狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來虎和狼的關係不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔爾艦隊發來通信表示抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標減速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要停船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想仔細看看對方的船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 若沒有我在 就只能全力逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 被抓住只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有我在船上 減速也就有了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是投降 或是獻上我乞求饒命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他三七二十一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有賭在逮捕我的瞬間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂破綻 都發生在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利多半還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要確認這一點就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是泰坦尼亞的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是泰坦尼亞的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞時刻需要有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事事關泰坦尼亞安泰和繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方收起了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不打算開火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要放我們一條生路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會從背後「砰」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿和方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 青史留名的二人首次意識到了彼此的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都因為我年輕而小覷我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人知道我的悲慘經歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天 要讓卿等都拜倒在我的腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(693,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}野望的前奏曲


